# Adobe Creative Cloud Plans - Supported Locales

## Overview
This document defines all supported locales for Adobe Creative Cloud pages (e.g., /creativecloud/plans.html).
Use these locale codes when writing tests, configuring monitoring, or developing locale-specific features.

## Locale Format
Locales follow the pattern: `/{locale}/` or `/{country}_{language}/`
- Base URL structure: `https://www.adobe.com/{locale}/creativecloud/plans.html`
- US locale has no prefix: `https://www.adobe.com/creativecloud/plans.html`

